  `Nr`(`Vx`):    `Nrefreshes` locs in database with `Vx` seconds left
  `Ns`:       (not yet used)

dark.locs stores additional fields on top of the ones from dark.scriptors:

  `Nwhn`: time in milliseconds `Nwhen` the data for this loc was last checked
  `Nwho`: user `Nwho` first uploaded the loc
  `Nwht`: `Nwhat` scripts the loc came from
